These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, july, march, february, september, december, november
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, photography, reading, sudoku, hiking, filmmaking, gardening
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, martial-arts, horror, superhero, adventure, romance
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching satire movies##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
14. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
15. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
19. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Birthday   | july | february         | november   | may | december    | september | march |
| Hobby         | reading | hiking | camping | photography | gardening  | filmmaking  | sudoku    |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero  | adventure         | satire     | thriller    | martial-arts | horror     | romance     |

