.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, journalist, analyst, fisherman, software-developer, security-guard, scientist
7 different pets are kept: fish, snake, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit, dog, goldfish
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, disco, indie, metal, pop, reggae, rock
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold, bellflower, azalea, rose, poppy, amaryllis
 1. the journalist is the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the fisherman is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the scientist##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the electrician is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the security-guard##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the electrician##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the owner of the goldfish##2
11. the fan of disco is the owner of the mouse##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the owner of the goldfish and the fan of reggae##2
14. the security-guard is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
15. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
16. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
17. the owner of the fish is on the left of the analyst##1
18. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
19. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
20. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who growspoppy and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
| Job      | software-developer   | analyst | electrician      | fisherman   | scientist     | security-guard    | journalist      |
| Pet          | fish    | snake     | hedgehog | goldfish | rabbit | dog  | mouse |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | indie         | metal    | ambient    | pop     | reggae     | disco     |
| Flower     | amaryllis | azalea     | marigold      | poppy       | daisy    | bellflower | rose    |

